name: The Mushroom
description:
It was build as a memory of those who died. Filled with the material from the impact zone the people thought it would make the structure function as some kind of good luck statue. The radioactive radiation instead killed more for each day. To bad the books about nuclear bombs were destroyed decades ago.

A piece of Journeys through memories.

The owner will be able to collect the uncompressed 2k 120fps video file and the image files used to render this animation. Each image is a scene of its own, worthy of being an own artwork.

Music by astrofreq.
